- Games with an average rating greater than 4 are considered highly rated by the users;
- Total play time and the number of games played are metrics that reflect user engagement and diversity in gaming activities.

sql:
SELECT favorite_game 
FROM users 
WHERE favorite_platform IN ('GENESIS', 'SUPER NINTENDO');

